@startuml
[*] --> InsertCard : Card is inserted
InsertCard --> PromptPIN : User prompted to enter PIN
PromptPIN --> VerifyPIN : PIN verification in progress
VerifyPIN --> Success : PIN verified successfully
Success --> Options : Provide options to the user
Options --> ApproveWithdrawal : User approves withdrawal request
ApproveWithdrawal --> ProcessWithdrawal : Withdrawal processing in progress
ProcessWithdrawal --> DispenseCash : Cash is dispensed
DispenseCash --> PrintReceipt : Receipt printing in progress
PrintReceipt --> ReturnCard : Card returned to user
ReturnCard --> ResetSystem : System resets and becomes ready for next user

VerifyPIN --> Failure : PIN verification failed
Failure --> PromptPIN : User prompted to re-enter PIN
PromptPIN --> VerifyPIN : PIN verification in progress (loop)

@enduml
